textAfterTable: Wonder Woman's comic debut came in a 1941 issue of All Star Comics. She would later inherit her own series and make several appearances in cartoons starting - most famously - with 1973's Super Friends. Her only successful venture into the live-action world came with the 1970's Wonder Woman TV series. The first video game she would be in was the 1995 SNES fighting game Justice League Task Force. Will she finally be able to carve out her own niche in fighting game history?
